President Muhammadu Buhari on Thursday met with some governors of the All Progressives Congress (APC) at the Presidential Villa in Abuja. They are Zamfara State Governor, Abdulaziz Yari, Jigawa State Governor, Abubakar Badaru and Kebbi State Governor, Abubakar Atiku Bagudu. The closed door meeting was still in progress at the time of filing this report.  Details later…